# Add your own favorite cigar brands to your liking! 

### **Basic product + sale filters**

'''
"Java Latte" cigars "on sale" | discount | clearance
'''

### **General sale/discount variants**

```
"Java Latte" cigars ("on sale" | discount | clearance | deal | promo | special | markdown | bargain | cheap | savings)
```

### **Add common retailer wording**

```
"Java Latte" cigars ("sale" | "price drop" | "limited time" | "today only" | "blowout" | "flash sale")
```

### **Target pages that list prices**

```
"Java Latte" cigars ("$" | price | "price list" | "per box" | "per pack")
```

### **Catch bundle/sampler deals**

```
"Java Latte" cigars (bundle | sampler | pack | multi-pack | variety | combo)
```

### **Look for coupon or promo code pages**

```
"Java Latte" cigars (coupon | "promo code" | voucher | discount code)
```

### **Target known cigar shops but keep it broad**

```
"Java Latte" cigars ("sale" | discount | clearance) site:.com
```

### **Search forum-style deal posts**

```
"Java Latte" cigars ("deal" | "on sale") (forum | reddit | discussion)
```

### **Search for reviews that mention pricing**

```
"Java Latte" cigars ("price" | "worth it" | "best deal" | "cheapest")
```
